Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}STUDENT COUNCIL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}TEENS LOVE BIBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, the headmaster confiscated it\Nfrom a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NSTILL HASN'T DONE IT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He said, "It's not proper reading material,\Nso dispose of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jeez. Why didn't he just do it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not proper reading material?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CRUDE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.28,RightSignM2,NTP,0,0,0,,LEWD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This country is becoming lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's got her skirt in a bunch?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe nudity with pubic hair?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane showed great interest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Kaguya, I wouldn't if I were you!\N- Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A survey. "When was your 'first time?'"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"By high school. 34%."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way! There's no way\Nthat many are doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}34%!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, more than a third!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}One out of three people\Nmeans there's a high likelihood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.69,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,DID IT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.69,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,DID IT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.69,LeftSignM4,NTP,0,0,0,,DID IT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}that one of these three\Nhave already had such an experience!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's only that high\Nbecause the respondents
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,are the people who read\Nthis kind of magazine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean "sample selection bias."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, there can't actually be\Nthat many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}This percentage seems about right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In fact, it's probably low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, I don't even think I need to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but have you had\Nthat kind of experience, Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, the first was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TOWN PAGES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh. The area code for Aomori is 017.\NThat's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't that normal\Nfor most high school students?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You two must not have been raised\Nin a loving environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Maybe I should hurry up\Nand get a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The area code for Oshamanbe\Nin Hokkaido is 01377... and 013...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Father would never allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Kaguya realizes there's a nervous\Ncomponent to their reactions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When humans realize\Nthey've gotten a late start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}compared to those around them,\Nthey get nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then that anxiety makes them\Nsuccumb to the emotional need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}of finding a romantic partner. In short...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm too late to the party?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I’M FALLING BEHIND?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO GET A GIRLFRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SHINOMIYA, GO OUT WITH ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinomiya, go out with me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Confess your love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya's objective of the day was decided.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The whole thing is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, President,\NI heard you were very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She instigates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She instigates some more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't have that kind of relationship\Nwith a particular person. Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Not right now"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}An expression that hints\Nat the existence of a girlfriend long ago,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but even if he's never gone out\Nwith anyone, it isn't a lie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an expression loved by people\Nthe world over, from the young to the elderly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! Miyuki Shirogane\Nhas never had a romantic experience!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet it can't be said\Nthat he isn't popular.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, he is quite popular.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps it should be said\Nbirds of a feather flock together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or perhaps we should consider that\Nin many cases, oddballs are drawn to oddballs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the trend is only dangerous\Ncharacters being attracted to you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}WHAT IS THIS HAIR?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}you won't reach a romantic relationship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}WHAT IS THIS SMOKE?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I so popular?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, despite having no experience,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane was supremely confident\Nin his own popularity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The women must be attracted\Nto my overflowing intelligence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Should I feel guilty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, this man possesses\Nboth boundless confidence and pure chastity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a combination that has made him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...a twisted monster virgin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh. Then of course you've done it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even that monster has a weakness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}MONSTER VIRGIN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is still a virgin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be easy to lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But telling an experienced person\Nthat I have experience{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}would be like a movie neophyte claiming\Nknowledge about movies to a film buff,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}thinking they can trick the person!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Supposing I did lie to her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have tons of experience!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're bragging about it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you that embarrassed\Nabout having your virginity exposed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'd see through me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-If you're that curious,\Nyou can always ask me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The best he can do is bluff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know you have a little sister, President,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so you probably\Ndo it with her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course not! Are you a moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did it to my newborn nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was videotaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a loon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not good to be excessively afraid\Nof physical contact with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess that's the dark side\Nof modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the dark side of the nobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You must do it a lot to your dog Pesu,\Ndon't you, Chika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- You do?\N- No! Please don't drag me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shinomiya family upbringing\Nis this perverse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so ignorant of the ways of the world\Nthat she thinks it's common sense?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know what it means\Nby "first time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please don't make light of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As a lady, I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's referring to kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the daughter\Nof the owner of a conglomerate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's been protected\Nfrom sexual information for 16 years now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The beginning and end\Nof her sexual education was kissing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}ALL ABOUT SEX\NPISTIL STAMEN\NWHEN YOU GET MARRIED,\NLEAVE IT TO THE MAN.\NTHE END
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything more than that\Nshe picked up from urban legends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}So the stork\Nhas nothing to do with it, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She's a "daughter in a box"\Ntaken to the extreme!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Naturally, she has no idea\Nwhat "your first time" refers to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President, I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In this case, "first time" means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,puts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,like beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MINUTES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the law is you do that kind of thing\Nafter you get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought my heart was gonna stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:02.93,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,RESULTS OF\NTODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}SHINOMIYA LOSES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}FOR INCREDIBLE IGNORANCE\NABOUT SEXUAL KNOWLEDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinomiya loses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}President, I disapprove\Nof illicit intercourse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So would you go do it to yourself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}KAGUYA WANTS\NTO BE FIGURED OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a quiet night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Fujiwara's turn to walk Pesu today,\Nso she had to go home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pesu! Pesu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And Ishigami was in and out of here\Nbefore I even noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He gets the perfect attendance award\Nin his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've mellowed out\Nsince we first started here, Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You mean I've gained weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, "mellow," not "marshmallow."\NYour personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like making small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been making an effort\Nto become slightly more likeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it also helps that I have a better\Nunderstanding of you as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We've been working together here\Nat student council for half a year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I have\Na pretty good understanding of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'll test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, let's test how much\Nyou really know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know the game "20 Questions"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}20 Questions!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:11:00.30,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,EXAMPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a game in which one player\Ngets 20 questions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Is it smaller than my palm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}to guess what the other player\Nis thinking of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Is it edible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the player can only ask questions\Nthat can be answered with a yes or no.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm thinking of an eraser.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the guesser gets it correctly\Nwithin 20 questions, they win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they can't, the other person wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But if you get 20 questions,\Nyou can pretty much guess it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you really know me, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you should be able to guess it\Nwith half that, ten questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}20 CHAMBER BELGIAN REVOLVER\N"HENRION, DASSY, AND HEUSCHEN"\N(BUT ONLY 10 BULLETS LOADED)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then my first question...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One, is it something that can be touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It isn't a word or concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Two, is it an electrical appliance?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Three, is it something that's warm or cold?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Considering her answers,\Nit could be a living thing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}WARM-BLOODED\NANIMAL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}FOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}food, a substance\Nlike warm water or ice,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOILING WATER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}ICE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a bonfire or some kind\Nof temperature control device?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}FIRE...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}ETC., ETC...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But since this is a test\Nof how well I understand Shinomiya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the answer must be something\Nconnected to Kaguya Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Four, is it something you own?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Five, is it something you touched today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Six, is it something that's at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Three noes in a row.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it was something Shinomiya\Npossessed, but now I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll explore Shinomiya's psychology\Na little more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seven, is it something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What is that expression?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looks kind of embarrassed or bashful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it a living thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down! Let's confirm it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can touch it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It isn't an electrical appliance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It isn't room temperature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinomiya doesn't own it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hasn't touched it,\Nand of course, it isn't in her house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all matches!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's something that Shinomiya likes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a roundabout confession of love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nine, in what way do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THUMP THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As a friend? As a human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can only answer with a yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm so flustered, I wasted a shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to calm down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's possible\Nthat the answer is someone else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ten, is it something\Nthat's very intelligent, handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}with somewhat light-colored hair\Nand well-defined eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's definitely me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez, Shinomiya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a twisted way to confess your love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been through a lot together, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every time, I understood more\Nabout the person named Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, you're out of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Give me your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a certain extent, I understand\Nwhat kind of person Shinomiya is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}At a time like this, she always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}PESU (DOG)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More precisely,\NFujiwara's dog, Pesu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Good boy! Good boy!\NYou're so cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}INTELLIGENT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}HANDSOME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}HANDSOME\NLIGHT-COLORED HAIR
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So shall we\Ngo home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}HANDSOME\NLIGHT-COLORED HAIR\NWELL-DEFINED EYES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's getting late, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The results of today's test...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.12,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BECAUSE WHEN ALL WAS SAID AND DONE,\NSHIROGANE UNDERSTOOD SHINOMIYA'S NATURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Pass.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}I FEEL LIKE PESU REMINDS ME\NOF SOMEONE...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}PANT PANT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Kaguya Shinomiya is the daughter\Nof the Shinomiya family,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}which was part of one\Nof the old financial combines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KAGUYA WANTS TO WALK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Her life was decided when she was born\Nor perhaps even before she was born.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For example, this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}2,574 times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the number of times{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya Shinomiya has gazed\Nout the window on the way to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SHINOMIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's lodged itself in there deep\Nnear the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll arrange for another car,\Nso if you would wait for a short while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll just walk there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At least go with Hayasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If she waits for me to change clothes,\Nshe'll be late,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I think she'll be fine\Ngoing on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There. You see? I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miss Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was slightly out of breath\Nas she ran under the refreshing sun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may never get the chance\Nto walk to school again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to take advantage\Nof this precious opportunity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I believe the president\Nrides his bike to school from Setagaya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}BICYCLE LANE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}so he probably takes Meiji Street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}MEIJI STREET
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The president always gets to school\Non the late side,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}so if I wait on the bridge, I'm sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if I don't hurry,\NI'll miss the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you've got a problem,\Nbriefly tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The pedestrian crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The pedestrian crossing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, I'll cross with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Would you let go of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are a lot of pedestrian crossings\Non the way to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}how did you go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}With a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeti always held my hand\Nwhen we crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Abominable Snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Her name is Ienaga,\Nso her nickname is Yeti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But now that we're in the upper grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,she said there's no more\Ngroup walking to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So now, I'm on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}WAAAH WAAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Her thinking is still totally lower grade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I had a better head on my shoulders\Neven when I was in the lower grades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want to be with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just because going to school in a group\Nis officially over,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean\Nyou have to walk to school by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should meet up somewhere\Nwith your friend
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,or pick her up at her house\Nand walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're smart! Are you a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mikiti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you're fine now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, genius girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning! Surprised to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning! You did surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Let's go to school together!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eight twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If they find out I was late,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll never be allowed\Nto go to school on my own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wanted to try doing it even just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Going to school with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The bell's gonna ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You, too. President, are you going to be—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not late yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never been late yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the problem, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you walk, you'll definitely be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}If a member of the Shuchiin\NStudent Council is late,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}it sets a bad example!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hop on the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We've gotta fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Being late is bad,\Nbut two people on a bike is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be quiet!\NWhen it comes to student council,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,school rules take priority\Nover traffic rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Days later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya has returned to her usual routine\Nof going to school by car.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Can I go to your house, Yeti?\N- Sure! Come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But sometimes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}she remembers that one day and smiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go back to the forest.
